law.history: Repealed 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 496, sec. 67, effective July 13, 1990. -- Amended 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 365, sec. 2, effective July 15, 1986. -- Amended 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 40, sec. 2, effective March 12, 1980. -- Created 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 212, sec. 4, effective June 17, 1978.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Personal service contract review subcommittee-- Objections or disapproval of contracts to be reviewed by secretary of finance and administration -- Monthly report.
